From Roy Radow Subject Re A loathesome subject In carlos Carlos Carrion writes In article Roy Radow writes But this does not imply that ALL relationships between youth and adults are exploitative and The critical factor here is whether the sexual activity is forced or whether it is an activity that is consensually agreed upon and freely engaged in by the people When a child is forced there is often damage on the other hand Wholeheartedly agree consensual relationships are often found to be positive experiences for all Why do I find this hard to believe Care to convince us Carlos Why not check out some of the scientific research that has been done in this area and convince Research around the world indicates that the issue of coercion is the critical For those interested in research on the topic I can suggest Li et al England Constantine United States and Sandfort The Netherlands I especially like Sandfort's research for he actually quotes what the boys who are involved in the relationships have to Children and Sex New Findings New Perspectives by Larry Constantine Floyd Martinson Little Brown Boston Boys On Their Contacts With Men by Theo Sandfort Global Academic Publishers Elmhurst New York Perspectives on Paedophilia by Brian Taylor Batsford Academic Educational London Paedophilia A Factual Report by Frits Enclave Rotterdam The Netherlands Sexual Experience Between Men and Boys by Parker Maurice Temple Smith Middlesex Great Britain Children's Sexual Encounters With Adults by Li West Gerald Duckworth London Yours in Liberation Roy Roy Radow panix roy North American Man Boy Love Association For a packet containing a sample Bulletin publications list and membership information send postage to NAMBLA Info PO Box Midtown Station NYC NY